<concept id="concept_jxh_qxr_kv">
 <title>Run Data Collector from Docker</title>
    <shortdesc>You can run the <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/> image
        from Docker Hub.</shortdesc>
 <conbody>
     <p><indexterm>Data
                    Collector<indexterm>Docker</indexterm></indexterm><indexterm>Docker<indexterm>Data
                    Collector</indexterm></indexterm>To run the <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            image from Docker Hub, use the following command in the Docker Quickstart
            Terminal:<codeblock>docker run -d -P --name streamsets-dc streamsets/datacollector</codeblock></p>
        <p>For more information about running <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            from Docker, see <xref href="https://hub.docker.com/r/streamsets/datacollector/"
                format="html" scope="external"/>.</p>
 </conbody>
</concept>
